WEBVTT

00:00:58.915 --> 00:01:01.561
I turned it on, and there it was:

00:01:02.061 --> 00:01:04.233
Ferguson, Missouri,

00:01:04.233 --> 00:01:05.815
Michael Brown,

00:01:06.445 --> 00:01:08.665
18-year-old black man,

00:01:08.665 --> 00:01:14.564
unarmed, shot by a white police officer,
laid on the ground dead,

00:01:14.564 --> 00:01:18.478
blood running for four hours

00:01:18.478 --> 00:01:22.993
while his grandmother and little children
and his neighbors watched in horror,

00:01:22.993 --> 00:01:24.989
and I thought,

00:01:26.019 --> 00:01:29.240
here it is again.

00:01:29.240 --> 00:01:32.962
This violence, this brutality
against black men